public interface MeetupsRegistrationModel
extends com.liferay.portal.model.AuditedModel, com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<MeetupsRegistration>

The base model interface for the MeetupsRegistration service. Represents a row in the "SN_SMILE_MeetupsRegistration" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

This interface and its corresponding implementation MeetupsRegistrationModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in MeetupsRegistrationImpl.

Author:
Brian Wing Shun Chan
See Also:
MeetupsRegistration, MeetupsRegistrationImpl, MeetupsRegistrationModelImpl
